'''菲律賓語'''（{{lang|fil|Pilipino}}或{{lang|fil|Wikang Filipino}}）是[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]的[[國家語言|國語]]，自1987年修訂之《[[菲律賓憲法|菲律賓憲法]]》規定為[[國家語言|國家語言]]。事實上，菲律賓語是標準化的[[他加禄语|他加禄语]]，[[馬可斯|馬可斯]]倒臺後在[[阿基諾夫人|阿基諾夫人]]推動之下成為菲律賓的國語。<ref>{{citation| url = http://www.chanrobles.com/article14language.htm| title = The Constitution of the Republic of the Philippines| date = 1987-02-02| accessdate = 2017-02-12| publisher = Chanrobles Law Library| article = Article XIV, Sections 6 and 7| language = en| archive-date = 2007-11-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071110234327/http://www.chanrobles.com/article14language.htm| dead-url = yes}}</ref>

